    "insurance_summary_document": "This case involves comprehensive orthodontic treatment for an adult patient addressing alignment concerns in both the upper and lower arches. The treatment will utilize clear aligner therapy, with a planned approach that includes staged tooth movements. Retention is bundled with the treatment, ensuring continued stability post-treatment. The monitoring approach will be a combination of remote check-ins and in-office reviews. Intraoral photographs and a panoramic X-ray have been utilized as diagnostic assets to aid in treatment planning.\n\n---\nThis summary is for administrative and insurance documentation purposes only. It does not guarantee insurance approval or coverage and should not be construed as a determination of medical necessity. The dentist remains the clinical decision-maker at all times.",
